 MSD calculations with ORION+TRISTAN                              6729 1451
 Heidelberg MSC calculations                                      6729 1451
 Exciton model calculations with code PCROSS                      6729 1451
 Cluster emission in terms of the Iwamoto-Harada model  with      6729 1451
 Kalbach systematics angular distributions (see RIPL-1)           6729 1451
 Mean free path parameter in PCROSS set to  1.3 (Default: 1.3)    6729 1451
